  <brief_title>STARR Trans-anal Resection Versus Vaginal Rectocele Repair Using Elevate: Effects on Defecatory Function</brief_title>
  <acronym>RectoVerso</acronym>
  <official_title>STARR Type Trans-anal Resection Versus Vaginal Rectocele Repair Using a Posterier Elevate Prothesis: a Randomized, Multicentric, Prospective Study on Defecatory Function</official_title>
